dataset.name: 承保项目信息明细
dataset.sql: SELECT a.sn as '序号',z.DEPTNAME ,b.A_ROLE_ID,b.B_ROLE_ID,e.BIZTYPE_ID,e.BIZVAR_ID,a.CUS_ID, f.IDCARDTYPE_ID,f.IDNUM,d.AREA_ID,g.ENTTYPE_ID,d.ENTPROPERTY_ID,d.ENTSCALE_ID, d.INDUTYPE_ID,h.AFLB_ID,i.UDTTOTLOC,i.UNDBDATE,i.UNDEDATE,i.BY3,k.TOTLOC as rt, a.APPTOTLOC - k.TOTLOC as tt , j.CAT3NAME,j.CAT2NAME,j.CAT1NAME,i.SN,i.ZHT,i.BZHT,concat(a.GATRATE,a.GATRATEU) as '担保费率', '实收费用总额','开票担保费','开票财务评审','开票咨询费','开票财务顾问费','开票其他费', '风险分担比例','是否纳入基金','贷款利率',a.UNDBDATE '承保开始日期',a.UNDEDATE '承保结束日期',a.by3 '承保期限（月）','贷款用途','基金名称','承保备注' FROM tbs.tbs_projundwrt a left join tbs.tbs_proj b on a.PROJ_ID = b.ID and b.DEL = 0 left join tbs.tbs_customer d on a.CUS_ID =d.ID and d.DEL = 0 left join tbs.tbs_projundwrt_bizvt e on a.ID = e.PROJUNDWRT_ID and e.DEL = 0 left join tbs.tbs_customer_idnum f on d.ID = f.CUS_ID left join tbs.tbs_customer_enttype g on d.ID = g.CUS_ID left join tbs.tbs_projundwrt_bank h on a.id = h.PROJUNDWRT_ID left join tbs.tbs_projundwrt_cfmar i on a.id = i.PROJUNDWRT_ID and i.DEL = 0 left join (SELECT sum(TOTLOC) totloc,proj_id,UNDWRT_ID FROM tbs_proj_release where del = 0 and valid = 1 group by UNDWRT_ID) as k on k.UNDWRT_ID = a.id left join tbs.v_cggall j on a.CUS_ID = j.CUSID left join tbs.bdf2_user x on x.id = b.A_ROLE_ID left join tbs.bdf2_user_dept y on y.USERNAME_ = x.USERNAME_ left join tbs.tbs_approver z on z.DEPTID = y.DEPT_ID_ and z.TITLE like '%经理%' and z.TITLE not like '%经理助理%' where a.DEL = 0 and a.VALID = 1 and i.UNDEDATE < :endDate and i.UNDBDATE > :beginDate and b.PROJ_NAME like '%' :proj_name '%' group by a.SN,j.SN
